# DozePlus

Lightweight and safe Android Doze optimization module for improved battery efficiency and idle behavior tuning.

---

## ⚙️ Features

- Optimizes Android Doze behavior
- Reduces background process load when device is idle
- Lightweight service-based execution
- No persistent background processes
- Safe and reversible changes

---

## 📱 Requirements

- Android 8.0+ (API 26+)
- Magisk installed
- Root access enabled

---

## 📦 Installation

1. Download the latest release
2. Open Magisk Manager
3. Install module from storage
4. Reboot device

---

## 🔧 How it works

DozePlus applies system tuning at boot using Magisk service scripts:

- Enables low power mode when device is idle
- Adjusts background process limits
- Restores normal behavior when device is active

---

## 📊 Behavior

| State   | Action Applied |
|--------|----------------|
| Sleep  | Battery optimized mode |
| Awake  | Normal system behavior |

---

## ⚠️ Notes

- This module does not modify system partitions
- All changes are systemless
- Designed for stability over aggressive tuning

---

## 🧪 Status

Work in progress (v1.0 base version)

